The Upstream-Clean Approach

HNSWlib's SpaceInterface has a method:
virtual void *get_dist_func_param() = 0;

This void* is passed as the third argument to every distance calculation. Instead of polluting the base class or using thread-local globals, you should use this pointer to pass a context struct.



